title: Hillel Hall, northwest corner Amsterdam Avenue and 109th Street; Plan of first floor; Plan of upper floors; Chester Hall, northwest corner Amsterdam Avenue and 107th Street; Plan of first floor; Plan of upper floors.

text:
221 West 109th Street, north side, west of Amsterdam Avenue. This is a ½-story and in the rear is a three-story frame house.

1932.

J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
